Slices are top level 'keys'
* SLICES = dogs and cats

state = {
   dogs: [
      {name: 'walter', color: 'white'},
      {name: 'sadie', color: 'orange'},
   ]
   cats: [
      {name: 'matice', color: 'white},
      {name: 'baloo', color: 'black'}
   ]
}


actions should only effect one slice at a time 

   const newDogAction = (dog) => {
      type: 'dog/addDog',
      payload: dog
   }

example actions:
   allRecipes/allRecipe - index 
   allRecipes/getRecipe - show 
   allRecipes/addRecipe - add 
   allRecipes/deleteRecipe - destroy 
   allRecipes/updateRecipe - edit 
   favoriteRecipes/addRecipe
   favoriteRecipes/delteRecipe
   searchTerm/setSearchTerm
   searchTerm/clearSaerchTerm
